      <item>
        <title>Project: Wordlist (in progress)</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;This week we started on our first major project on redesigning a website from one of the local restaurants. We picked a restaurant and will have 5 responsive web pages redesigned at the end. This series of blog posts will document my process from beginning to end. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The first step in our project is creating a word list of everything we can think of about the restaurant. I picked Tarka. Here are a list words I came up with (I will add more later). &lt;/p&gt;

